              ></path>
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
                d="M20 1C21.6569 1 23 2.34315 23 4V20C23 21.6569 21.6569 23 20 23H4C2.34315 23 1 21.6569 1 20V4C1 2.34315 2.34315 1 4 1H20ZM20 3C20.5523 3 21 3.44772 21 4V20C21 20.5523 20.5523 21 20 21H4C3.44772 21 3 20.5523 3 20V4C3 3.44772 3.44772 3 4 3H20Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-2/3 md:pl-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-800 dark:text-white mb-3">
        About Me
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        I am currently undertaking an integrated degree apprenticeship in
        digital marketing and I would like to develop my skills in web development to complement the skills that I am acquiring. In the near future, I would like to expand these skills to become more full-stack oriented, taking on a variety of projects to demonstrate my expertise.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-800 dark:text-white mb-1">
        Skills
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3  text-sm">
        My skills are limited, but I am currently learning...
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
        <span
          class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm transition duration-150 ease-out hover:ease-in hover:bg-blue-900 hover:text-white"
          >HTML</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm transition duration-150 ease-out hover:ease-in hover:bg-blue-900 hover:text-white"
          >CSS</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm transition duration-150 ease-out hover:ease-in hover:bg-blue-900 hover:text-white"
          >Tailwind</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm transition duration-150 ease-out hover:ease-in hover:bg-blue-900 hover:text-white"
          >Svelte</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm transition duration-150 ease-out hover:ease-in hover:bg-blue-900 hover:text-white"
          >Python</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm transition duration-150 ease-out hover:ease-in hover:bg-blue-900 hover:text-white"
          >Astro</span
        >
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-800 dark:text-white mb-3">
        Contact Information
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-indigo-800 dark:text-blue-700"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            fill="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z"
            ></path>
            <path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <a href="mailto:hello@jackstirzaker.com" class="hover:underline"> hello@jackstirzaker.com </a>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-indigo-800 dark:text-blue-700"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            fill="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Worcestershire, UK
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out forwards;
  }
</style>

